--------------------------------- NEW FEATURES --------------------------------
ALL of the following NEW features for FA-18 Interceptor are now available using
the Amiga Smart Port from IDD!
  1.    Support of ANALOG JOYSTICK!! Provides more sensitive control, adds the
        full analog range (0-251) of the AMIGA Smart Port for better control.
  2.    Auto-Sensing of an Amiga Smart Port in analog mode with automatic
        software switching between digital and analog joysticks modes.
  3.    Joystick centering function to provide exact centering which can be
        used at anytime... Even during flight!
  4.    Dynamic Joystick Scaling - The IDD Upgrade will adjust the control
        scale to use the full capabilities of your joystick to obtain maximum
        performance simply by moving your joystick!
  5.    Joystick and rudder sensitivity Setting - You can use any one of 20
        sensitivity settings per axis. Use the one you need to suit the speed
        of your machine and your personal preference! Switch between them at
        any time!
  6.    Support for ANALOG PEDALS!! This feature contains the same centering
        and dynamic scaling features used with the joystick. Analog Pedal and
        Rudder inputs can be reversed for wiring compatibility.
  7.    Support for ANALOG THROTTLE!!  Now you can quickly and easily move
        between throttle settings without going to the keyboard.
  8.    Support for FOUR BUTTONS!! Users of two joysticks or joysticks with 4
        buttons can now use the extra buttons to reduce the need to access the
        keyboard.
  9.    Ability to reverse the Throttle/Rudder inputs for wiring compatibility.
 10.    Adjustable dead zone around center for the joystick and pedals to
        allow for variations in the centering.
 11.    Support for "VIEWS ON THE JOYSTICK"!! Allows use of the CH FlightStick
        Pro "HAT" switch to provide view switching without using the keyboard.
 12.    Select between two styles of viewing which be assigned to the "HAT"
        switch when using a CH FlightStick PRO.

